sentences.english: Objective To evaluate the anatomy and HRCT findings of foramen of nasal bone.
sentences.chinese: 目的探討鼻骨孔的解剖基礎及影像學表現。

sentences.english: Endoscopic technique is an ideal way in the treatment of nasal bone fracture.
sentences.chinese: 鼻內鏡技術是治療鼻骨骨折較爲理想的方法。

sentences.english: Results 350 cases were found with bilateral fracture of nasal bone.
sentences.chinese: 其中350例診斷爲雙側鼻骨骨折。

sentences.english: Objective Discussion on cadet nasal bone fracture in simple effective diagnosis method.
sentences.chinese: 目的探討軍校學員鼻骨骨折的簡便有效診治方法。

sentences.english: Discussion on Reduction Methods of Monteggia Fracture;
sentences.chinese: 尋找鼻骨骨折復位的有效方法。

sentences.english: Objective To probe into the significance of thin layer CT in the nasal bone fracture diagnosis.
sentences.chinese: 目的探討薄層CT掃描在鼻骨骨折診斷中的意義。

sentences.english: It is proved that DR imaging is an ideal method of nasal bone examination.
sentences.chinese: 結果表明DR攝影是鼻骨常規檢查的理想手段。

sentences.english: The consonants at the end of the English words sun , sum , and sung are nasals .
sentences.chinese: 輔音結束時的英文單詞太陽，總之，和成是鼻骨。

sentences.english: Results Foramen of nasal bone were revealed linear shadow in axial and coronal images.
